I was wondering what the process for taking a leave of absence is. I know according to @1600 that I can click on cancel registration but I dropped all my classes and the cancel registration button still has not showed up yet and so it's a little alarming right now. It is late but I could not go in to cancel my registration in person today because of the holiday. I'm in the college of L&S. Thank you so much!
